item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】PACK - Nickelodeon's Grachi (Discography) 4 albums + Rarities (FLAC, ALAC & MP3)
item.description:
Grachi it's Nickelodeon's most successful latin TV series, with 3 seasons and a couple movies and TV specials.

Grachi released 1 album per season, but Nickelodeon helped the main star Isabella Castillo to make her debut as a solo popstar after the end of Grachi, so her album it's also included in this post.

TAKE IN COUNT THAT NOT ALL THE SONGS ARE LOSSLESS!!!
These albums aren't available anymore for streaming, nor for sale, this pack is a mix of the songs in the highest quality possible and a lot of rarities, region restricted tracks, demos, etc.

Luckily, most of them are in FLAC and ALAC quality! Yas
